The '''Magic Guild Store''' is located on the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}} of the [[Wizards' Guild]]. One must have a [[Magic]] level of 66 to enter the guild. The store is owned by [[Wizard Sinina]]. He sells [[Mystic robes|blue mystic robes]]. He also sells the [[Magic cape|Magic skillcape]] to players who have achieved 99 [[Magic]].

==Stock==
{{StoreTableHead|sellmultiplier=1000|buymultiplier=600|delta=1}}
{{StoreLine|name=Mystic hat|stock=1000|restock=100}}
{{StoreLine|name=Mystic robe top|stock=1000|restock=100}}
{{StoreLine|name=Mystic robe bottom|stock=1000|restock=100}}
{{StoreLine|name=Mystic gloves|stock=1000|restock=100}}
