===Magic cape===
If a player has 99 [[Magic]], they will have access to a duplicate version of the shop, with the only difference being the addition of the [[Magic cape]]. The stock of this shop is '''not''' shared with the regular shop.
{{StoreTableHead|sellmultiplier=1000|buymultiplier=600|delta=1|hidecaption=y}}
{{StoreLine|name=Magic cape|smwname=Magic cape#Untrimmed|buy=N/A|stock=1|restock=1|gemw=no}}
{{StoreTableBottom}}
===Magic cape(t)===
For players with 99 [[Magic]] and at least one other [[Skill mastery|99]], they will access a second duplicate shop. Just like the previous, the stock of this shop is not shared with the others.
{{StoreTableHead|sellmultiplier=1000|buymultiplier=600|delta=1|hidecaption=y}}
